                                "stop": 8.369,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 62213,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 02-1183, United States against Patane will be announced by Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.369,
                        "stop": 196.145,
                        "byte_start": 62213,
